messages.text: Sweet Jesus, Em, is this for real?!
as far as I can tell
What r u talking about? Where r u?
Pls tell me ur closer to Houston.
but I can still see them
Lots of them…way off in the distance.
I’m so glad you’re alive, Em.
same here! I was so worried about you!
why didn’t you answer my texts??
I was kinda busy trying to stay alive
Nope. I ran out of gas.
God damn, girl! Hitch a fucking ride!!!
But get in a vehicle and get the fuck moving.
And the bombs are far away.
U can’t GET far enough away from a NUCLEAR BOMB!!
What are they saying on CNN?
That ur a stubborn idiot. It’s all over the news.
where else are they planning to drop the nukes?
If ur west of Brenham, ur pretty well fucked..
Sign says 5 miles to Prairie View.
But u need to get ur ass here to Houston.
We all thought u were dead.
Me and my mom, Christian and Sgt. Delaney…
Yeah, his dad got us off the base last night
Did he say anything about me?
he wouldn’t shut up about you
He begged his dad to go back and get you
But Christian told me he loved me earlier
But isn’t Sgt. Delaney your dad’s best friend?
and he was SUPPOSED to take me to Dallas to meet my dad
but he drove me south instead
It was insane there last night.
he knew where he was going.
No one is telling me shit dude.
But it might explain why he was so pissed.
he got back here a while ago and talked to Christian.
Christian told him u were in range of the bombs
but that u refused to keep driving.
he was kinda mad when u weren’t at my house last night.
That’s why he came to my house.
Why he would want to come for me specifically?
God damn zombies were running all over Texas killing everyone in sight.
I guess. But something feels really off… Besides the obvious.
What do you know about this virus?
Or whatever the fuck it is?
Only the bits I get from Wolf Blitzer…
but the fucking army isn’t telling CNN much.
the Wolf said it has something to do with microscopic algae.
first, the virus kills the human body as we think of it…
then it feeds on some genetically modified algae…
and this algae creates electricity which keeps the body functioning…
Well…I got straight D’s in chem and biology, so…
No. But from what I’ve SEEN…
these aren’t your rotten, foot dragging run-of-the-mill Walking Dead zombies…
they’re straight up 28 Days Later whack jobs.
More similar to drones or evil robots tbh.
Like Christian's dad when he’s in a bad mood – fucking G.I. Joe.
I can’t believe my parents were part of this.
I’m so sorry about your mom, Ada.
But she wasn’t who I thought she was.
Ada, please… it’s me ur talking to.
None of us in the classified corner of that base actually believed
that our parents held the boring ass jobs they claimed to
but to be the cause of the fucking apocalypse?!
In the last text he sent he sounded really freaked.
He said THEY were about to get him.
I’ve been texting him all day but haven’t gotten an answer.
There’s no way he’s alive and not in contact with me.
And tell NO ONE I'm alive.
